         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Aug. 6th ¶ 1892 ¶ My dear Baron ¶  ¶ I regret to say that I have not been able to answer your note sooner, having a bad attack of gout in my right arm &amp; hand, many thanks for the Characeae Pt 1. ¶ Nor...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">92.08.06a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Edward Ramsay</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Universitetsbibliothek, Handskr. avdl., Lund.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style=""/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS is attached to M to O. Nordtedt, 8 August 1892<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(in this edition as 92-08-08a). Letterhead: 'Australian Museum Sydney'.</p>
               </note>Aug. 6th</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">1892</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">My dear Baron</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I regret to say that I have not been able to answer your note sooner, having a bad attack of gout in my right arm &amp; hand, many thanks for the Characeae Pt 1.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Nordstedt (1891).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>If it does not come to more that 20s/ or 30s/ a year I would like to take it — I will try this season to get the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Claudea</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>again, we have only had two or three trawling trips, and nothing worthy of mention among the Algae, was obtained.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have a few specimens put away some where which I will look up the first chance I get but I have no doubt when the warm weather comes around again, as I know the exact spot I shall be able to send you fresh specimens<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M had asked frequently for specimens of the alga bearing fruiting bodies since 1882:<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>see M to E. Ramsay 22 September 1882 (in this edition as<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>82-09-22c);<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the most recent known request was in M to E. Ramsay, 4 September 1891.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">believe me</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>dear Baron</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>yours sincerely</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ed. P Ramsay</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plantnames"
               style="font-style: italic; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Claudea</p>
